Reasoning: The paper discusses the extension of a task execution framework to enable loosely coupled programming on petascale systems, which involves distributed computing and parallel processing. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing). Other likely sub-categories include cs.Distributed (Distributed Systems), cs.PF (Performance), cs.SE (Software Engineering), and cs.SC (Supercomputing).
